AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000260> "A plan is a realizable entity that is the inheres in a bearer who is committed to realizing it as a completely executed planned process."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000119> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000260> "branch derived"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000260> "plan"@en)
