AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000524> "assembling process"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000524> "An assembling process is a manufacturing process that mounts or demounts components."@en)
